<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.1.4">
<l>maiyār kaṇmaṭa vāycciyar makkaḷai maiyaṉmai ceytavar piṉpōy</l>
<l>koyyār pūntukil paṟṟit taṉiniṉṟu kuṟṟam palapala ceytāy</l>
<l>poyyā vuṉṉaip puṟampala pēcuva puttakat tukkuḷa kēṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>aiyā vuṉṉai yaṟintukoṇ ṭēṉuṉak kañcuva ṉammam taravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Infatuating the simple herding ladies with kohl-full eyes,</l>
<l>[you] follow after them plucking and grabbing</l>
<l rend="indent">at their beautiful flowered saris,</l>
<l>[but] remaining alone, you commit more and more offences.</l>
<l>Liar! I have heard so much slanderous talk about you</l>
<l rend="indent">it could be a book!</l>
<l>Lord! I have come to know you,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] I am afraid to give you [my] breast.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
